bsbview - graphical viewer
--------------------------
- add ability to zoom in further than one-to-one pixel by scaling pixels

Batch processing
----------------
- add command line options to conversion tools to more easily permit batch
  conversions, for example *.KAP or everything in a given directory.  This
  has been requested by WIN32 users who cannot use a shell to do this.
  
GeoTIFF support
---------------
- add conversion to and from GeoTIFF format which is an open standard
